      <prop type="x-translation-ref">二子乘舟.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>二子乘舟，汎汎其景，願言思子，中心養養。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The two youths got into their boats,
Whose shadows floated about on the water.
I think longingly of them,
And my heart is tossed about in uncertainty.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
