      <prop type="x-translation-ref">二子乘舟.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>二子乘舟，汎汎其逝，願言思子，不瑕有害。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The two youths got into their boats,
Which floated away on the stream.
I think longingly of them,
Did they not come to harm?</seg>
      </tuv>
